True to the Best of my Knowledge.
1. This certificate is issued on the basis of the unaudited books of account of the Joint - Promoters and share of expenses incurred by them.
The joint promoters have not executed ATS for Plots A1 to A5 as also the actual amount received towards the booked inventory exceeds the estimated unit values submitted during the registration and changes have been affected accordingly in the unit values.

The amounts have been duly deposited in the Designated RERA Bank Account however only the transactions of 70% account have been reported here and certified

Since the project plot sale and is divided between 2 promoters. The reconciliation is not properly done by their internal auditor and consultant.
